node.title: All-rounder Santner unleashes with bat, as Brave capture Super Smash men's title
node.description: The all-rounder clobbered nine sixes in his near-century knock.
node.content: ["Blackcaps all-rounder Mitch Santner has demonstrated his power-batting ability, leading Northern Brave to the Super Smash T20 men's title with a 56-run win over Canterbury Kings at Hamilton.", "More to come\u00a0"]
